channel.title: Error when compiling
channel.description:
[code]NPCHandler.java:1126: cannot find symbol symbol : method randomKBD() location: class Item2 ItemHandler.addItem(Item2.randomKBD(), npcs[NPCID].absX, npcs[NPCID].absY, 1, Ge tNpcKiller(NPCID), false); ^ Note: stream.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. 1 error Files Compiled Successfully! Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
Why can't it "find" the symbol?
if it helps this is whats giving the erros, if you cant see it there..
[code]if(npcs[NPCID].npcType == 50) { ItemHandler.addItem(Item2.randomKBD(), npcs[NPCID].absX, npcs[NPCID].absY, 1, GetNpcKiller(NPCID), false); }[/code]
